pokedexEntries.red: Appears in filthy areas. Thrives by sucking up polluted sludge that is pumped out of factories.
pokedexEntries.blue: Appears in filthy areas. Thrives by sucking up polluted sludge that is pumped out of factories.
pokedexEntries.yellow: Made of hardened sludge. It smells too putrid to touch. Even weeds won't grow in its path.
pokedexEntries.gold: As it moves, it loses bits of its body from which new Grimer emerge. This worsens the stench around it.
pokedexEntries.silver: Wherever Grimer has passed, so many germs are left behind that no plants will ever grow again.
pokedexEntries.crystal: When two of these Pokémon's bodies are combined together, new poisons are created.
pokedexEntries.ruby: Grimer's sludgy and rubbery body can be forced through any opening, however small it may be. This Pokémon enters sewer pipes to drink filthy wastewater.
pokedexEntries.sapphire: Grimer emerged from the sludge that settled on a polluted seabed. This Pokémon loves anything filthy. It constantly leaks a horribly germ- infested fluid from all over its body.
pokedexEntries.emerald: Born from polluted sludge in the sea, Grimer's favorite food is anything filthy. They feed on wastewater pumped out from factories.
pokedexEntries.fireRed: Sludge exposed to X rays from the moon transformed into Grimer. It loves feeding on filthy things.
pokedexEntries.leafGreen: Appears in filthy areas. It thrives by sucking up polluted sludge that is pumped out of factories.
pokedexEntries.diamond: It was born when sludge in a dirty stream was exposed to the moon's X-rays. It appears among filth.
pokedexEntries.pearl: It was born when sludge in a dirty stream was exposed to the moon's X-rays. It appears among filth.
pokedexEntries.platinum: It was born when sludge in a dirty stream was exposed to the moon's X-rays. It appears among filth.
pokedexEntries.heartGold: As it moves, it loses bits of its body from which new Grimer emerge. This worsens the stench around it.
pokedexEntries.soulSilver: Wherever Grimer has passed, so many germs are left behind that no plants will ever grow again.
pokedexEntries.black: It was born when sludge in a dirty stream was exposed to the moon's X-rays. It appears among filth.
pokedexEntries.white: It was born when sludge in a dirty stream was exposed to the moon's X-rays. It appears among filth.
pokedexEntries.black2: Born from sludge, these Pokémon now gather in polluted places and increase the bacteria in their bodies.
pokedexEntries.white2: Born from sludge, these Pokémon now gather in polluted places and increase the bacteria in their bodies.
pokedexEntries.x: Sludge exposed to X-rays from the moon transformed into Grimer. It loves feeding on filthy things.
pokedexEntries.y: Appears in filthy areas. It thrives by sucking up polluted sludge that is pumped out of factories.
pokedexEntries.omegaRuby: Grimer's sludgy and rubbery body can be forced through any opening, however small it may be. This Pokémon enters sewer pipes to drink filthy wastewater.
pokedexEntries.alphaSapphire: Grimer emerged from the sludge that settled on a polluted seabed. This Pokémon loves anything filthy. It constantly leaks a horribly germ- infested fluid from all over its body.
pokedexEntries.sun: Its main source of food is the slimy industrial waste of factories. This Pokémon's numbers have been decreasing in recent years.
pokedexEntries.moon: It was born from sludge transformed by exposure to X-rays from the moon. When its internal load of germs decreases, it dies.
pokedexEntries.ultraSun: It was born from sludge on the ocean floor. In a sterile environment, the germs within its body can’t multiply, and it dies.
pokedexEntries.ultraMoon: The wastewater coming from factories is clean these days, so Grimer have nothing to eat. They’re said to be on the verge of extinction.
